{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup mascarpone cheese, at room temperature\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 cup sour cream\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/caper/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 capers}}, rinsed, drained, coarsely chopped and dried on paper towels\
{\listtext	\'95	}Kosher salt and freshly ground black pepper\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 ounces {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/smoked-salmon/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 smoked salmon}}, cut into 3/4-inch pieces\
